msg: CAMEL-3250: Applied patch with thanks to Daniel Bevenius.

author: markt
msg: Enforce the rules in the JSP specification for parsing the attributes of custom and standard actions that require that the attribute names are unique within an element and that there is whitespace before the attribute name. The whitespace test can be disabled by setting the system property org.apache.jasper.compiler.Parser.STRICT_WHITESPACE to false

author: markt
msg: When removing a Host via JMX, do not attempt to destroy the host's pipeline twice.
